Class BaseImageDirectory

java.lang.Object
  |

All Implemented Interfaces:
Workspace
Deprecated. - the class has been deprecated, see Content API.

public class BaseImageDirectory
extends Object
implements Workspace

This helper class functions as the Workspace for a file system directory that contains geo-referenced image files. Various file types can be "detected" within a directory, by first registering the file type along with the file type of a coresponding ESRI "world file", via the static method registerType().
